## 2. Non-Flat Relational Alignment (Congress Structure)

```plaintext
         [Shared Node X]
           /    |    \
       (No flattening)
       /      |      \
  [H3]      [A2]     [E2]
```

- Each intelligence contributes **irreducible structure** to the shared node  
- No graph is overwritten  
- The shared node becomes a **story node** traversable by each graph, using its own logic

